title: Green Frog
description: A close-up image of a vibrant green frog with distinctive orange webbed feet. The frog is positioned against a white background, showcasing its smooth skin texture and large, expressive eyes.

title: Coastal Bird Scene
description: A vibrant coastal scene featuring various birds in flight and on the ground. The background showcases a clear blue sky and a serene ocean with gentle waves. Cliffs and greenery are visible on the shore, while several birds, including a tern and a seagull, are depicted in different poses. A crab is also seen on the beach, adding to the lively atmosphere of the natural setting.
